比人捉去青山瞓一排<br />\n而家諗返自己真喺痴痴地線<br />\n自己比錢自己洗<br />\n咪即係去自己鋪頭買野..."},{"pid":"41585c3e6950af206f49f3802c2a4036f6e8cbca","tid":713907,"uid":55511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:12:50.000Z","msg":"因為genes相似會提高相互吸引力<br />\n冇一齊住好似有另一個解釋"},{"pid":"595982ae8a368fdf19783b0b4e357cce899be340","tid":713907,"uid":2638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:44:25.000Z","msg":"條囡後生應該好得<br />\n佢細佬型到..."},{"pid":"fd76e6ca0e05e2a2626869f3775f98f358a15f66","tid":713907,"uid":49918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:49:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d05fa3d7087a304a3866ac3f69d169236e68b47f","tid":713907,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"595982ae8a368fdf19783b0b4e357cce899be340","tid":713907,"uid":2638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:44:25.000Z","msg":"條囡後生應該好得<br />\n佢細佬型到..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:53:27.000Z","msg":"Agger, 2002年重逢先35歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樓上嘅連登仔應該望住張相，幻想後生16年嘅佢同型棍細佬亂倫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}